text: Dinagat can refer to: ==Places in the Philippines== * Dinagat Islands, a province in the Philippines ** Dinagat Island, primary/main island of the province ** Dinagat, Dinagat Islands, a municipality in the province * Dinagat Sound, body of water between the islands of Dinagat and Siargao ==See also== * Dumagat (disambiguation)
title: Dinagat
